# ğ‡ğ–-ğ“ğğğ‹ğŠğˆğ“ - A multi-option hacking toolkit for Termux

#color codes for styling
GRY='\033[1;30m'
RED='\033[0;31m'
BLU='\033[0;34m'
GRN='\033[0;32m'
